    <section name="Introduction">

      <subsection name="What is the Gallery Picker Plugin?">
        <p>The Gallery Picker Plugin provides an "imagelink" plugin that can
        be added to any editing template. This allows CMS users to easily select an image
        from the gallery and include it in a document.</p>
      </subsection>

      <subsection name="Screenshots">
        <p>The imagelink plugin ready to be included in any editing template:</p>
        <p><img src="images/imagelink.png" alt="imagelink field type in template editor"/></p>
        <p>Image Preview in a document:</p>
        <p><img src="images/imagepreview-selected.png" alt="Image Preview in editing template"/></p>
      </subsection>

      <subsection name="Getting started">
        <p>
          <a href="install.html">Install</a> the Gallery Picker Plugin, and
          <a href="usage.html">use it</a>!
        </p>
